{"tid":97711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文推特以英、日文拜年 中國網友批漢奸","createTime":"2017-01-27T23:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T06:48:45.000Z","uid":35790,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4260239fce4db3b37ab59feba18e5c3ebb5fb4d","tid":97711,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T23:58:53.000Z","msg":"蔡英文推特英、日文拜年 中國網友批漢奸<br />\n<br />\n2017/01/27 23:20&nbsp;5949<br />\n<br />\n台灣總統英蔡英文今天中午在推特以英文及日文雙語，向海外網友祝賀雞年，結果此舉又讓中國網友「玻璃心」粉碎，紛紛留言痛批。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文在推特先以英文說：「From the people of Taiwan, we wish everyone a bright and prosperous Year of the Rooster.」（台灣人民祝大家雞年飛黃騰達）。<br />\n<br />\n之後又用日文寫：日本の皆様、今年は実のある素晴らしい一年となりますよう、心よりお祈り致します。（衷心祝福各位日本朋友，能有非常出色的一年）。<br />\n<br />\n中國《環球網》報導這則消息時強調，不少（中國）網友批評：蔡英文祝賀中國農曆<span style=\"color: red;\">新年，「為何不寫中文？」蔡英文的推特也被洗版，有人質疑：「蔡英文和台北市長柯文哲為什麼都堅持用英文更新內容？難道這是『推特外交』？</span>可我覺得，外交場合見到的那些人未必有時間follow你，而你的選民們卻會天天有時間吐槽你。」<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">還有中國人怒批蔡英文是「漢奸」：「日本人又不過春節，你用日語幹什麼！為什麼向日本示好？難道你已經把台灣寶島被日本強佔、島民造屠殺的歷史忘記了嗎？</span></span>」不過，蔡英文的個人臉書則用中文拜年：「新年希望 2017未來一起。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170127/1045170/蔡英文推特英、日文拜年　中國網友批漢奸\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fhot%2F20170127%2F1045170%2F%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%E8%8B%B1%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E6%96%87%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E6%89%B9%E6%BC%A2%E5%A5%B8&d=VeVOV7LkbUF9DlidzKtQe5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7e63178f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20170127/1045170/蔡英文推特英、日文拜年　中國網友批漢奸</a>"},{"pid":"4dd06e438314dfdd2d9b60a5faac68701a5ba940","tid":97711,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T23:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170127/640_2509be0e661bec5f031065d80fb07858.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170127%2F640_2509be0e661bec5f031065d80fb07858.jpg&h=18218ddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef8e3eb54959beda84ca7aa698899d590e435712","tid":97711,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"改名啦漢奸"},{"pid":"99afe764d0335ad01fba1f0b43a2fabc9895d52d","tid":97711,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"人地都唔認自已係漢人<br />\n何來有漢奸？"},{"pid":"a3bd5e4174160c3f4e881021b102e6d852d03bab","tid":97711,"uid":23832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地都唔認自已係漢人<br />\n何來有漢奸？</blockquote><br />\n佢好似係客家人<br />\n咁你覺得客家人算唔算支那中原漢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a2cea130bb76046f9aa9eaad78fc6898bd4859","tid":97711,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地都唔認自已係漢人<br />\n何來有漢奸？</blockquote><br />\n佢好似係客家人<br />\n咁你覺得客家人算唔算支那中原漢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劉邦漢族人係魏晉南北朝已被殺光"},{"pid":"5d502d7edb9285072599ee8d55526ccb686538d4","tid":97711,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:27:54.000Z","msg":"好似係毛魔帶日本人侵華<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f22bc2bd65c314d8d65d67721097f09a8d31a7","tid":97711,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:33:41.000Z","msg":"咁佢個名叫英文丫麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e26eac4270d0859c92fbedc7b431aa2f582628d","tid":97711,"uid":78009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"Twitter係咁玩，通用語言唔是中文"},{"pid":"40ee1541c2d6657474a25b9dde86eb77077f5835","tid":97711,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201